@startuml frontend_backend_flow
title Frontend ↔ Backend Communication

skinparam participant {
    BackgroundColor #e3f2fd
    BorderColor #1565c0
}

participant "Frontend\n(React)" as F
participant "Backend\n(FastAPI)" as B

F -> B : HTTP Request\n(GET/POST + JSON)
activate B
B -> B : Validate & Process
B --> F : HTTP Response\n(JSON + Status Code)
deactivate B

note right of B
  **Validation:**
  • Pydantic models
  • Type checking
  
  **Errors:**
  • 4xx: Client error
  • 5xx: Server error
end note

@enduml
